{"tid":1054744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮又地震 傳訊總監、空軍部長請辭","createTime":"2019-03-10T05:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T11:24:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"70ddb35c8df17f991a340344fbaebf5af4e4bb5f","tid":1054744,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:16:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190310/20630086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190310%2F20630086&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2DBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=8beb5032\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190310%2F20630086&h=52e664a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190310/20630086</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白宮又地震 傳訊總監、空軍部長請辭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190310/large/10wx05p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190310%2Flarge%2F10wx05p.jpg&h=6092b691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國白宮再現離職潮，霍士前聯席總裁夏因（Bill Shine，圖）前日辭任白宮傳訊總監，同日空軍部長威爾遜（Heather Wilson）亦宣佈請辭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夏因加入特朗普競選團隊<br />\n<br />\n白宮發聲明指，夏因將加入特朗普明年競逐連任的競選團隊擔任高級顧問。特朗普讚揚夏因工作表現出色，稱期待與他在明年競選活動合作。夏因稱「服務總統和國家是一生人最有滿足感的經歷」，但期望花更多時間陪伴家人。<br />\n<br />\n但消息人士指，特朗普近期不滿夏因未能為他改善媒體形象，對他已失信心，極度依賴白宮發言人桑德斯處理傳訊工作，夏因上月亦未有陪同特朗普出席美朝峯會。55歲的夏因去年7月上任，是特朗普的第五任傳訊總監，前四任的任期短至兩周至三個月。<br />\n<br />\n威爾遜則宣佈將出任德州大學艾爾帕索分校校長。58歲的她前年5月上任，指為了讓空軍平穩過渡，將於5月31日才離任。她是自前國防部長馬蒂斯辭任後，另一名辭職的國防部高層。她被認為原本有可能接任馬蒂斯，成為美國首位女國防部長，但特朗普至今仍未提名任何人接替。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/路透社/法新社/英國《泰晤士報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n北韓疑部署試射導彈 美警告加強制裁<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n委恢復供電 反對派上街聲討馬杜羅"},{"pid":"7b0a27b054855a0d0142b5954c30dc6105df9d57","tid":1054744,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:32:17.000Z","msg":"炒哂啲左膠就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6de203613a0f55feecef7608841df3bb3ae971","tid":1054744,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T11:20:56.000Z","msg":"有冇熟美國政治人士講解下"},{"pid":"77adb0c7265f410d2bbd2ae4e6bc083751fe5614","tid":1054744,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T11:23:01.000Z","msg":"好在係美國, 唔係的話就慢慢變成抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c77b7cccce43534b3e0b563d2ad42f6ad9b1888","tid":1054744,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b0a27b054855a0d0142b5954c30dc6105df9d57","tid":1054744,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T05:32:17.000Z","msg":"炒哂啲左膠就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T11:24:18.000Z","msg":"夏因唔係左膠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}